 -*NOT* Summon Item <br><br>Affliction Haste - +33% Spell Haste - Detrimental ONLY - MIN Cast Time: 3 sec - MIN Dur.: 36 sec <br>Extended Affliction - +20% Spell Duration - Detrimental ONLY - MIN Dur.: 36 sec <br>Affliction Efficiency - -25% Mana Cost - Detrimental ONLY - MIN Dur.: 36 sec <br><br>Summoning Haste - +30% Spell Haste - Summon Pet ONLY <br>Reanimation Haste - +30% Spell Haste - Summon Skeleton Pet ONLY <br>Summoning Efficiency - -25% Spell Mana Cost - Summon Pet ONLY <br>Reanimation Efficiency - -25% Spell Mana Cost - Summon Skeleton Pet ONLY <br><br><br>Explaination Summary: <br>Hastes = Do not effect CH heals <br>(15%)(30%) Do not effect Spells with less than 3sec cast time <br>(30%) Do not effect Spells that last less than 72 secs <br><br>DD Damage Amps = PB AoEs are not Amplified <br>Target AoEs are not Amplified <br>DoT Damage is not Amplified <br><br>DoT Damage Amp = DoT does 'x' more tics of damage for whatever last tic did in damage <br>Only works on DoTs that last more than 36 seconds (nearly all DoTs) <br><br>Enhancement = Buffs and Heals (not CH heals) <br>Affliction = DoTs (not DD or AoE) <br>Pet Summons = Necros get different summon foci than all other pet classes? /shrug <br><br><br><br><br>Basically Complete Heal(spell), Complete Heal(BP effect), and all other forms of Complete Heal <br>are excluded from Focus Effects, but this was known anyways and is only being included in summary <br>because it is a common exclusion.<br><br><br>Elder Fatsow<br>60 Ogre Shaman <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub19.ezboard.com/uduranstorm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>duranstorm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wolf Elemental</span><br>  Posts: 175<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(6/5/02 9:15:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub19.ezboard.com/funconqueredfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=176.topic&index=1>Reply</a> 